    bf:tableOfContents [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "Innehåll: Under the street lamp / Joe Bataan with group -- Yes. I'm ready / The Hesitations -- You're gonna make it / The Festivals -- I don't have you / The Continental 4 -- The third degree / The Sequins -- Never my love / The Magictones -- No you for me / The Climates -- Here it comes / The Persians -- Chapel bells are calling / The Insiders -- That ain't the way / The determinations -- Keep on trying / The Invincibles -- Betcha' can't guess who / The Newcomers -- Never will I (make my baby cry) / The Magnificent Seven -- I like the way you love me / Foxy -- Someone else's arms / Channel 3 -- Won't you please be my girl / The Soulville All-Stars -- Daydreamer / C C and Company -- I'm still here / The Notations -- A girl from a country town / Lee Williams & THe Cymbals -- No one else will do / The Dynamic Tints -- Love me girl / The Mylestones -- I had the whole world to choose from (and I chose you) / The Fantastic Four -- So glad you're home / The Superbs -- Things will be better / The Just Brothers." ] ;
